(1,17,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,'Sky Diving','Adventure','sky-diving','<p><span style=\"color:rgb(120,120,120);font-family:Jost, sans-serif;\">Ski touring is a form of skiing where participants travel across snow-covered terrain using skis. It often involves traversing backcountry or off-piste areas, away from ski resorts.</span><span style=\"font-size:1rem;\">Embark on an unforgettable journey through the breathtaking landscapes of the Northern San Francisco Bay, where nature\'s grandeur meets serene tranquility. This time-saving tour offers the perfect opportunity to experience some of the region\'s most iconic and awe-inspiring highlights, from the towering redwoods to the peaceful shores of the bay.<br><br></span>Start your adventure by stepping into the mystical world of the giant redwoods. These ancient trees, some over a thousand years old, create an almost otherworldly atmosphere with their massive trunks and lofty canopies that seem to touch the sky. </p>','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8YC-0auiWBw&pp=ygUnYnVuZ2VlIGp1bXBpbmcgcGxhY2Vob2xkZXIgbm8gY29weXJpZ2h0','Frequently Asked Questions','{\"1\":{\"title\":\"What is paragliding?\",\"content\":\"Paragliding is a recreational and competitive sport where participants fly lightweight, free-flying, foot-launched glider aircraft with no rigid structure.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"Is paragliding safe?\",\"content\":\"Paragliding is generally safe when proper training, certified equipment, and safety protocols are followed. The risk increases with adverse weather conditions, poor equipment maintenance, or lack of skill.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Do I need prior experience to try tandem paragliding?\",\"content\":\"No, tandem paragliding does not require any experience. A certified pilot handles the flight while you enjoy the ride.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"Do I need to be physically fit for paragliding?\",\"content\":\"You don\\u2019t need to be an athlete, but moderate fitness is necessary for running during launch and landing, and carrying gear.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Can I paraglide in any weather?\",\"content\":\"No, paragliding requires calm to moderate winds, no rain, and stable atmospheric conditions. Adverse weather can be dangerous.\"}}',1,1,5,2,300.00,300.00,250.00,25,1,'{\"1\":{\"name\":\"Lunch Subsidies\",\"price\":\"50\",\"unit\":\"fixed\",\"price_type\":\"per_person\"}}',NULL,46,67,79,'1230','-25.274399','-115.171921','Include Features','{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Ski Touring Involves Exploring Remote, Off-Piste Terrains Away From Ski Resorts.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"A Full-Body Workout Combining Skiing, Hiking, And Endurance.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Engaging In Challenging Ascents And Thrilling Descents On Various Terrains.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"Enjoying Pristine Landscapes And Serene Natural Environments.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Carrying Safety Gear (Avalanche Transceivers, Shovels, Probes) And Knowledge Of Rescue Procedures.\"}}','Exclude Features','{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Ski Touring Typically Avoids The Amenities And Maintained Slopes Found In Ski Resorts.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"It Steers Clear Of Crowded Slopes And Lift Systems.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Ski Touring Often Involves More Challenging And Varied Terrains, Less Suitable For Beginners.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"In Case Of Emergencies, Immediate Assistance May Not Be Readily Available Compared To Ski Resorts.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Unlike Ski Resorts, Conditions In Backcountry Areas Can Vary Significantly And May Not Be Groomed Or Controlled.\"}}','Highlights Of the Tour','{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Immersion In Breathtaking, Untouched Landscapes Away From Crowded Ski Resorts.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"Combining Endurance And Skill While Exploring Diverse Terrains.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Accessing Pristine, Less-Traveled Areas For A Unique Adventure.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"Strengthening Camaraderie Among Fellow Skiers In A Shared Outdoor Experience.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Accomplishing Challenging Ascents And Thrilling Descents In Natural Settings.\"},\"6\"