h and landing, and carrying gear.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Can I paraglide in any weather?\",\"content\":\"No, paragliding requires calm to moderate winds, no rain, and stable atmospheric conditions. Adverse weather can be dangerous.\"}}',1,1,5,3,700.00,0.00,200.00,1,2,'null',NULL,19,82,83,'32535','-25.274399','-115.171921','Include Features','{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Ski Touring Involves Exploring Remote, Off-Piste Terrains Away From Ski Resorts.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"A Full-Body Workout Combining Skiing, Hiking, And Endurance.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Engaging In Challenging Ascents And Thrilling Descents On Various Terrains.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"Enjoying Pristine Landscapes And Serene Natural Environments.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Carrying Safety Gear (Avalanche Transceivers, Shovels, Probes) And Knowledge Of Rescue Procedures.\"}}','Exclude Features','{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Ski Touring Typically Avoids The Amenities And Maintained Slopes Found In Ski Resorts.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"It Steers Clear Of Crowded Slopes And Lift Systems.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Ski Touring Often Involves More Challenging And Varied Terrains, Less Suitable For Beginners.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"In Case Of Emergencies, Immediate Assistance May Not Be Readily Available Compared To Ski Resorts.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Unlike Ski Resorts, Conditions In Backcountry Areas Can Vary Significantly And May Not Be Groomed Or Controlled.\"}}','Highlights Of the Activities','{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Immersion In Breathtaking, Untouched Landscapes Away From Crowded Ski Resorts.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"Combining Endurance And Skill While Exploring Diverse Terrains.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Accessing Pristine, Less-Traveled Areas For A Unique Adventure.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"Strengthening Camaraderie Among Fellow Skiers In A Shared Outdoor Experience.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Accomplishing Challenging Ascents And Thrilling Descents In Natural Settings.\"},\"6\":{\"title\":\"Feeling The Elements And Connecting With The Mountains In A Profound Way.\"},\"7\":{\"title\":\"Experiencing The Freedom Of Traveling Through Snowy Wilderness On Skis.\"}}',NULL,'null','[\"5\",\"4\",\"6\",\"2\",\"8\",\"7\",\"9\"]','Activities-01-1738150980.webp',NULL,1,40,'2025-01-29 11:43:00','2025-04-23 05:24:16');
