(13,25,'Diani','<p>Diani is one of the most beautiful beach towns in Kenya. It is found along the South Coast, about 30km from Mombasa. The beach is clean, the water is clear, and the vibe is peaceful — perfect for relaxing, taking a walk by the ocean, or enjoying water activities like jet skiing, snorkeling, and sky diving.</p><p>Diani is also known for its lively resorts, beach bars, and fun holiday experiences. Whether you are traveling with family, as a couple, or just looking for a solo escape, Diani offers a mix of fun and calm. You can explore places like Colobus Monkey Sanctuary, Kaya Kinondo Forest, or take a dhow trip to Wasini Island nearby. If you\'re looking for a perfect holiday spot at the Coast, Diani never disappoints.</p>','Diani','en','2025-05-15 08:33:25','2025-05-15 08:33:25');
