(77,7,'faq','b2c264c','{\"main_title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"faqs\":{\"1\":{\"title\":\"1. What services does your travel agency offer?\",\"description\":\"We provide customized travel packages, flight and hotel bookings, guided tours, travel insurance, visa assistance, and more. Whether you\\u2019re looking for a family vacation, honeymoon, adventure trip, or business travel, we\\u2019ve got you covered!\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"2. How do I book a trip with your agency?\",\"description\":\"Booking a trip with us is easy! You can contact us through our website, call our customer support, or visit our office. Our travel experts will help design the perfect itinerary based on your preferences and budget.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"3. Do you offer customized travel packages?\",\"description\":\"Yes! We specialize in tailor-made travel experiences. Just share your interests, travel dates, and budget, and we will create a personalized itinerary for you.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"4. Can you help with visa applications?\",\"description\":\"Yes, we provide visa assistance for various destinations. Our team will guide you through the documentation process and requirements, but final approval depends on the respective embassy.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"5. Do you offer travel insurance?\",\"description\":\"Yes, we recommend purchasing travel insurance to cover unexpected events such as trip cancellations, medical emergencies, and lost luggage. We can assist in arranging the best insurance plans for your trip.\"},\"6\":{\"title\":\"6. What payment methods do you accept?\",\"description\":\"We accept various payment methods, including credit\\/debit cards, bank transfers, and online payment platforms. Some destinations may also require advance deposits for bookings.\"},\"7\":{\"title\":\"7. What happens if my flight gets canceled or delayed?\",\"description\":\"In case of flight cancellations or delays, we assist in rebooking your tickets, arranging alternative flights, and coordinating with airlines to minimize inconvenience. Travel insurance may also help cover additional costs.\"},\"8\":{\"title\":\"8. Can I make changes to my booking after confirmation?\",\"description\":\"Yes, changes can be made, but they may be subject to airline, hotel, or tour operator policies. Fees may apply depending on the type of change and the time before departure. Contact us as soon as possible for assistance.\"},\"9\":{\"title\":\"9. Do you offer group travel discounts?\",\"description\":\"Yes, we provide special discounts for group bookings, corporate trips, and family vacations. Contact us for exclusive group travel deals.\"},\"10\":{\"title\":\"10. How can I stay updated on travel deals and promotions?\",\"description\":\"You can subscribe to our newsletter, follow us on social media, or check our website regularly for the latest travel deals, discounts, and exclusive offers.\"}}}',1,1,'2025-01-30 11:26:51','2025-01-30 11:30:39'),
